<inglise> Commission Regulation (EC) No 2293/2000 </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 2293/2000, </eesti>
<inglise> of 16 October 2000 setting the maximum amount of compensatory aid resulting from the conversion rates for the Swedish krona and the pound sterling applicable on 1 August 2000 </inglise>
<eesti> millega s&auml;testatakse 1. augustil 2000 kohaldatavatest Rootsi krooni ja naelsterlingi vahetuskurssidest tuleneva tasandustoetuse &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;r 16. oktoober 2000 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 2799/98 of 15 December 1998 establishing agrimonetary arrangements for the euro(1), and in particular Article 5(2) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 15. detsembri 1998. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 2799/98, millega kehtestatakse p&otilde;llumajanduse eurol p&otilde;hinev valuutakord, (1) eriti selle artikli 5 l&otilde;iget 2, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas: </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) Article 5(1) of Regulation (EC) No 2799/98 provides that compensatory payments may be made in cases where the exchange rate applicable on the date of the operative event is below that previously applicable. However, that provision is not applicable to amounts to which a rate lower than the new rate was applicable during the 24 months immediately before the new rate took effect. </inglise>
<eesti> 1) m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2799/98 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikes 1 n&auml;hakse ette, et tasandustoetust v&otilde;ib maksta juhul, kui rakendusjuhu kuup&auml;eval kohaldatav vahetuskurss on varem kohaldatud kursist madalam; k&otilde;nealust s&auml;tet ei kohaldata summade puhul, mille suhtes 24 kuu jooksul vahetult enne uue kursi kehtestamist kohaldati sellest madalamat kurssi; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) The exchange rates for the Swedish krona and the pound sterling applicable on the operative event date of 1 August 2000 were lower than those previously applicable. </inglise>
<eesti> 2) rakendusjuhu kuup&auml;eval, 1. augustil 2000 kohaldatud Rootsi krooni ja naelsterlingi vahetuskursid olid varem kohaldatud kurssidest madalamad; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) The compensatory aid is to be determined and paid in accordance with Regulation (EC) No 2799/98 and Commission Regulation (EC) No 2808/98 of 22 December 1998 laying down detailed rules for the application of the agrimonetary system for the euro in agriculture(2), as amended by Regulation (EC) No 1410/1999(3). </inglise>
<eesti> 3) tasandustoetus m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks ja seda makstakse vastavalt m&auml;&auml;rusele (E&Uuml;) nr 2799/98 ja komisjoni 22. detsembri 1998. aasta m&auml;&auml;rusele (E&Uuml;) nr 2808/98, milles s&auml;testatakse p&otilde;llumajanduse eurol p&otilde;hineva valuutas&uuml;steemi &uuml;ksikasjalikud rakenduseeskirjad p&otilde;llumajandussektoris, (2) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1410/1999; (3) </eesti>
<inglise> (4) The measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinions of the Management Committees concerned, </inglise>
<eesti> 4) k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las asjaomaste korralduskomiteede arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The maximum amounts of the first tranche of compensatory aid which may be paid as a result of the reduction recorded on the operative event date of 1 August 2000 in the exchange rates for the Swedish krona and the pound sterling compared to the exchange rates previously applicable are listed in the Annex. </inglise>
<eesti> Tasandustoetuse esimese osa &uuml;lemm&auml;&auml;rad, mida v&otilde;idakse maksta rakendusjuhu kuup&auml;eval, 1. augustil 2000 registreeritud Rootsi krooni ja naelsterlingi vahetuskursside registreeritud alanemise tulemusel varem kohaldatud kursside suhtes, loetletakse k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the seventh day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub seitsmendal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 16 October 2000. </inglise>
